            "id": 6410604,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 廣穎(4973)股價拉至漲停，漲停價76.2元，成交6,867張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>廣穎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4973:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4973\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4973-TW</a>)08日12:57上漲6.9元，股價漲停報76.2元，委買5,000張、委賣2,000張，成交6,867張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為快閃記憶體相關產品之製造及買賣。記憶體模組之製造及買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>廣穎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4973:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4973\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4973-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲12.14%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲5.81%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-2,478 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-2,425 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-53 張</li> <li>融資增減：-327 張</li> <li>融券增減：-50 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
